00:13:56,030 --> 00:13:57,750
if Hao Qianqian could come,

298
00:13:58,150 --> 00:13:59,750
he hoped the three of you

299
00:13:59,750 --> 00:14:01,200
could continue cooperating with him

300
00:14:01,200 --> 00:14:01,870
by singing.

301
00:14:03,270 --> 00:14:04,670
Qian just had a baby.

302
00:14:04,720 --> 00:14:05,550
She can't come.

303
00:14:07,150 --> 00:14:07,790
You see,

304
00:14:08,670 --> 00:14:10,320
we worked together before.

305
00:14:10,630 --> 00:14:12,200
He couldn't be too direct with you.

306
00:14:13,080 --> 00:14:14,840
The waitresses who worked here before

307
00:14:14,910 --> 00:14:15,870
were all his relatives.

308
00:14:16,000 --> 00:14:17,270
And their wages are very low.

309
00:14:17,630 --> 00:14:18,320
A few days ago,

310
00:14:18,320 --> 00:14:19,550
an elder at home passed away.

311
00:14:19,630 --> 00:14:20,550
They all went back.

312
00:14:20,630 --> 00:14:21,390
With the funeral over,

313
00:14:21,390 --> 00:14:22,510
they'll be back tomorrow.

314
00:14:24,000 --> 00:14:24,630
I know.

315
00:14:25,390 --> 00:14:26,550
Juan and I don't plan

316
00:14:26,550 --> 00:14:27,600
to stay here long-term.

317
00:14:28,720 --> 00:14:30,030
So, what is

318
00:14:30,030 --> 00:14:30,840
your next plan?

319
00:14:31,200 --> 00:14:32,630
Maybe you should think

320
00:14:32,630 --> 00:14:33,670
about what I said before.

321
00:14:33,870 --> 00:14:34,670
You've changed

322
00:14:34,670 --> 00:14:35,960
several jobs this year.

323
00:14:35,960 --> 00:14:37,390
You've had enough setbacks now.

324
00:14:37,440 --> 00:14:37,960
It's easier

325
00:14:37,960 --> 00:14:39,200
for you to connect with people.

326
00:14:39,390 --> 00:14:40,960
It'll surely help
with recruiting students!

327
00:14:41,150 --> 00:14:41,630
Get lost.

328
00:14:42,670 --> 00:14:43,080
Wait...

329
00:14:43,080 --> 00:14:44,480
Hey, no need to be mad.

330
00:14:44,720 --> 00:14:45,790
I'm being polite enough.

331
00:14:46,440 --> 00:14:47,670
You're really annoying!

332
00:14:48,240 --> 00:14:50,200
I know, I'm quite a detestable guy.

333
00:14:50,240 --> 00:14:51,080
But I only mean

334
00:14:51,080 --> 00:14:52,360
well for you.

335
00:14:52,630 --> 00:14:54,390
I'm really trying to help you.

336
00:14:54,440 --> 00:14:55,550
I really think my proposal

337
00:14:55,550 --> 00:14:56,200
is great.

338
00:14:56,240 --> 00:14:57,720
But I can only do this with you.

339
00:14:57,840 --> 00:14:59,390
No one else can achieve

340
00:14:59,390 --> 00:15:00,670
the effect I want.

341
00:15:00,720 --> 00:15:02,320
After all, dropping out of college...

342
00:15:02,320 --> 00:15:03,840
If you don't go, I'll really get mad.

343
00:15:05,200 --> 00:15:06,390
Fine, fine. Just calm down.

344
00:15:06,390 --> 00:15:07,030
Don't get angry.

345
00:15:08,150 --> 00:15:08,630
Listen,

346
00:15:08,790 --> 00:15:10,510
I'll give you my number.

347
00:15:10,600 --> 00:15:11,720
You should give me yours.

348
00:15:11,790 --> 00:15:12,720
-We've known...
-No need.

349
00:15:13,630 --> 00:15:14,030
Wait.

350
00:15:14,080 --> 00:15:14,870
We still don't have

351
00:15:14,870 --> 00:15:16,030
each other's numbers.

352
00:15:19,960 --> 00:15:20,550
Take it slow.

353
00:15:32,080 --> 00:15:32,720
Hello.

354
00:15:35,550 --> 00:15:36,000
Here.

355
00:16:12,870 --> 00:16:14,550
Why is that guy so creepy?

356
00:16:14,550 --> 00:16:15,600
Always staring at us.

357
00:16:17,390 --> 00:16:18,200
He's a regular customer.

358
00:16:18,240 --> 00:16:19,360
The manager specifically said

359
00:16:19,480 --> 00:16:20,240
not to offend him.

360
00:16:20,480 --> 00:16:21,390
Come on. Let's go.

361
00:16:39,960 --> 00:16:40,790
Yes, hello?

362
00:16:41,360 --> 00:16:43,840
Send a mosquito coil to room 2213.

363
00:16:44,240 --> 00:16:44,960
Room 2213.

364
00:16:45,240 --> 00:16:45,750
Mosquito coil.

365
00:16:46,030 --> 00:16:47,000
Coming right up.

366
00:16:48,030 --> 00:16:49,390
It's that bearded guy. I'll go.

367
00:16:49,480 --> 00:16:50,240
It's fine.

368
00:16:50,510 --> 00:16:51,480
You haven't had lunch yet.

369
00:16:51,480 --> 00:16:52,360
But I've finished mine.

370
00:16:52,870 --> 00:16:53,480
Don't worry.

371
00:16:59,480 --> 00:17:00,630
Here's your mosquito coil.

372
00:17:01,200 --> 00:17:01,870
Come in.

373
00:17:02,200 --> 00:17:03,080
The door is open.

374
00:17:08,030 --> 00:17:08,640
Sir,

375
00:17:09,270 --> 00:17:10,830
I'll leave it by your door.

376
00:17:11,640 --> 00:17:13,750
Light it for me. I've got no matches.

377
00:17:26,110 --> 00:17:26,720
Sir,

378
00:17:27,510 --> 00:17:28,590
I lit the mosquito coil.

379
00:17:28,880 --> 00:17:29,640
Please let me out.

380
00:17:29,960 --> 00:17:30,510
Hey, no rush.

381
00:17:30,920 --> 00:17:32,070
Have a seat, miss.

382
00:17:32,440 --> 00:17:33,310
I have other work to do.

383
00:17:35,030 --> 00:17:35,550
Hey, girl.

384
00:17:35,550 --> 00:17:37,030
How much do you make in a day?

385
00:17:37,160 --> 00:17:37,790
Sit down.

386
00:17:38,270 --> 00:17:40,920
I'll pay you 200 yuan, okay?

387
00:17:41,550 --> 00:17:43,270
I've been watching you for days.

388
00:17:43,720 --> 00:17:45,200
That other girl with you

389
00:17:45,200 --> 00:17:46,270
is also pretty.

390
00:17:46,440 --> 00:17:47,030
But you,

391
00:17:47,030 --> 00:17:48,590
you are just my type.

392
00:17:49,240 --> 00:17:49,790
Stay with me.

393
00:17:49,790 --> 00:17:50,680
Hey! Stay back!

394
00:17:52,790 --> 00:17:53,830
Get out of the way!

395
00:17:56,310 --> 00:17:59,030
Hey, girl, don't be so fierce.

396
00:17:59,270 --> 00:18:01,200
I'm really into you.

397
00:18:01,440 --> 00:18:01,880
Here,

398
00:18:02,920 --> 00:18:03,480
200 yuan more.

399
00:18:03,480 --> 00:18:05,440
Get lost! Touch me,

400
00:18:05,440 --> 00:18:06,550
and I'll send you to jail!

401
00:18:09,350 --> 00:18:10,400
I'm just kidding.

402
00:18:10,920 --> 00:18:11,640
Why so upset?

403
00:18:13,350 --> 00:18:14,920
You're such a disappointment.

404
00:18:34,440 --> 00:18:35,640
Why did you fire Li Juan?

405
00:18:36,030 --> 00:18:36,920
Customer complaint.

406
00:18:37,830 --> 00:18:39,000
Was it that guy from room 2213?

407
00:18:42,960 --> 00:18:43,830
I knew it!

408
00:18:44,480 --> 00:18:45,920
He sexually harassed Li Juan.

409
00:18:46,000 --> 00:18:46,880
We were already generous

410
00:18:46,880 --> 00:18:48,070
not to call the police on him.

411
00:18:48,070 --> 00:18:49,110
Yet he dared to complain?

412
00:18:49,270 --> 00:18:51,030
If the police came, I wouldn't intervene.

413
00:18:51,070 --> 00:18:52,720
But you didn't call them.

414
00:18:52,920 --> 00:18:54,550
So I have to handle the complaint.

415
00:18:55,070 --> 00:18:56,310
Li Juan is in her trial period.

416
00:18:56,480 --> 00:18:57,880
With a complaint, she must be fired.

417
00:18:58,000 --> 00:18:58,750
That's clearly

418
00:18:58,750 --> 00:18:59,920
stated in the contract.

419
00:19:00,440 --> 00:19:01,790
No matter what, she's your employee!

420
00:19:02,030 --> 00:19:02,590
Manager,

421
00:19:02,720 --> 00:19:03,640
you're also a woman.

422
00:19:03,750 --> 00:19:05,270
Shouldn't you protect our employees?

423
00:19:06,110 --> 00:19:07,880
I only work for the boss.

424
00:19:08,200 --> 00:19:09,200
This talk is meaningless.

425
00:19:09,240 --> 00:19:09,830
Get back to work.

426
00:19:10,440 --> 00:19:11,030
And Li Juan,

427
00:19:11,110 --> 00:19:12,240
go settle your pay and leave.

428
00:19:15,440 --> 00:19:16,110
I quit too!

429
00:19:16,350 --> 00:19:17,240
What are you doing?

430
00:19:18,030 --> 00:19:19,070
Suit yourself.

431
00:19:19,350 --> 00:19:20,480
It's not hard to hire

432
00:19:20,480 --> 00:19:21,160
another waitress.

433
00:19:21,480 --> 00:19:21,830
Oh, right.

434
00:19:22,070 --> 00:19:23,400
Since you resigned

435
00:19:23,550 --> 00:19:24,920
on your own, not dismissed,

436
00:19:24,960 --> 00:19:25,960
I'll cut half your pay.

437
00:19:26,000 --> 00:19:27,070
What gives you the right?

438
00:19:27,160 --> 00:19:28,480
I'll also file a complaint.

439
00:19:28,590 --> 00:19:29,350
I'll file a complaint

440
00:19:29,350 --> 00:19:30,550
with the authority against you.

441
00:19:31,640 --> 00:19:32,960
You're quite something!

442
00:19:37,680 --> 00:19:38,750
Fine, forget it.

443
00:19:39,070 --> 00:19:40,030
I won't deduct your pay.

444
00:19:40,110 --> 00:19:41,750
Just take the money and don't come back.

445
00:19:41,830 --> 00:19:42,510
It's too late.

446
00:19:42,510 --> 00:19:43,160
I'll file

447
00:19:43,160 --> 00:19:44,240
a complaint no matter what.

448
00:19:44,510 --> 00:19:45,240
-Come on.
-Just wait.

449
00:19:51,550 --> 00:19:52,200
Wanzhi,

450
00:19:53,750 --> 00:19:54,640
I'm sorry.

451
00:19:58,070 --> 00:19:58,750
Li Juan,

452
00:20:00,000 --> 00:20:01,000
let's agree that

453
00:20:01,400 --> 00:20:02,960
no matter what happens in the future,

454
00:20:04,070 --> 00:20:05,310
we won't blame

455
00:20:05,830 --> 00:20:07,240
or apologize to each other.

456
00:20:07,960 --> 00:20:08,480
Okay?

457
00:20:11,750 --> 00:20:12,270
Fine.

458
00:20:13,030 --> 00:20:14,400
Let's not talk about this now.

459
00:20:15,400 --> 00:20:16,480
What should we do next?

460
00:20:17,030 --> 00:20:18,680
Keep looking for jobs.

461
00:20:19,440 --> 00:20:20,440
We've been

462
00:20:20,440 --> 00:20:21,720
at the job market for three days.

463
00:20:21,720 --> 00:20:22,880
But we haven't found any jobs.

464
00:20:22,880 --> 00:20:24,200
We're just wandering now.

465
00:20:25,000 --> 00:20:25,510
Be patient.

466
00:20:26,030 --> 00:20:27,160
We can work part-time jobs

467
00:20:27,200 --> 00:20:28,000
until the New Year.

468
00:20:28,550 --> 00:20:30,110
That will be a good time to find jobs.

469
00:20:31,550 --> 00:20:32,200
But I need

470
00:20:32,400 --> 00:20:34,160
to spend New Year with

471
00:20:34,160 --> 00:20:35,160
Zhou Shuchun's mother,

472
00:20:35,590 --> 00:20:36,680
then visit my parents

473
00:20:36,680 --> 00:20:37,640
and siblings

474
00:20:37,640 --> 00:20:38,680
back home.

475
00:20:38,960 --> 00:20:39,920
Same as last year.

476
00:20:40,160 --> 00:20:41,160
I'll find a job first.

477
00:20:41,350 --> 00:20:43,160
Aren't you going back for New Year?

478
00:20:43,160 --> 00:20:43,790
Your dad...

479
00:20:46,350 --> 00:20:47,110
If I go back,

480
00:20:47,110 --> 00:20:48,880
he'll force me into college.

481
00:20:49,400 --> 00:20:50,000
I won't go back.

482
00:20:50,640 --> 00:20:51,200
But if you don't,

483
00:20:51,200 --> 00:20:52,440
your dad will be sad.

484
00:20:56,000 --> 00:20:57,270
Not until I've done better.

485
00:21:04,590 --> 00:21:05,310
It's okay.

486
00:21:06,720 --> 00:21:07,270
It's fine.

487
00:21:07,790 --> 00:21:09,270
Not a big deal.

488
00:21:09,310 --> 00:21:10,750
We'll just keep looking,

489
00:21:10,750 --> 00:21:11,310
right?

490
00:21:15,960 --> 00:21:17,000
Mr. Xiao?

491
00:21:17,510 --> 00:21:18,270
Wanzhi,

492
00:21:19,550 --> 00:21:20,480
you finally came back.

493
00:21:21,270 --> 00:21:22,400
Why are you here?

494
00:21:22,790 --> 00:21:23,830
I came with your dad.

495
00:21:24,400 --> 00:21:25,070
Where is he?

496
00:21:30,750 --> 00:21:31,350
Over there.

497
00:21:46,310 --> 00:21:46,960
Mr. Meng?

498
00:21:47,720 --> 00:21:48,440
Mr. Meng,

499
00:21:51,510 --> 00:21:52,440
Wanzhi is back.

500
00:21:54,200 --> 00:21:54,830
Oh, Wanzhi.

501
00:21:55,750 --> 00:21:56,480
You see,

502
00:21:57,440 --> 00:21:58,640
you didn't come back before.

503
00:21:59,400 --> 00:22:00,960
So I wanted to take a short rest.

504
00:22:01,000 --> 00:22:02,000
But I fell asleep.

505
00:22:03,640 --> 00:22:04,310
Li,

506
00:22:05,350 --> 00:22:06,480
please don't mind me.

507
00:22:06,680 --> 00:22:07,960
Of course not, Mr. Meng.

508
00:22:08,270 --> 00:22:09,240
Let's not stay here.

509
00:22:09,270 --> 00:22:09,830
Go inside.

510
00:22:10,590 --> 00:22:11,070
Okay.

511
00:22:18,030 --> 00:22:18,720
Mr. Meng,

512
00:22:19,000 --> 00:22:19,640
Mr. Xiao,

513
00:22:20,030 --> 00:22:20,750
have some tea.

514
00:22:21,030 --> 00:22:21,680
Thank you.

515
00:22:22,200 --> 00:22:23,240
I have neurasthenia.

516
00:22:23,350 --> 00:22:24,030
I can't drink tea.

517
00:22:24,750 --> 00:22:25,310
Li,

518
00:22:26,030 --> 00:22:27,070
I want to buy something,

519
00:22:27,440 --> 00:22:28,720
but I don't know where the store is.

520
00:22:29,160 --> 00:22:30,030
Can you show me the way?

521
00:22:32,880 --> 00:22:33,440
No problem.

522
00:22:42,960 --> 00:22:43,550
Have a seat.

523
00:22:56,550 --> 00:22:58,400
Living here alone...

524
00:22:59,680 --> 00:23:00,400
Wanzhi,

525
00:23:02,240 --> 00:23:03,240
is everything okay?

526
00:23:08,400 --> 00:23:10,030
Have you had dinner?

527
00:23:11,550 --> 00:23:13,400
I'll treat you to seafood.

528
00:23:14,240 --> 00:23:15,160
No time for that.

529
00:23:16,680 --> 00:23:17,750
I need to head out

530
00:23:18,350 --> 00:23:19,350
in 40 minutes.

531
00:23:21,110 --> 00:23:22,350
I just want to tell you

532
00:23:22,350 --> 00:23:23,240
something important.

533
00:23:23,790 --> 00:23:24,880
About your college...

534
00:23:27,030 --> 00:23:28,440
I already said it before,

535
00:23:29,110 --> 00:23:30,310
I won't go back to college.

536
00:23:30,720 --> 00:23:32,590
Are you here with Mr. Xiao

537
00:23:32,720 --> 00:23:34,160
to take me back this time?

538
00:23:34,590 --> 00:23:36,070
That's an abuse of power.

539
00:23:37,830 --> 00:23:39,400
I'm not here for you, really.

540
00:23:39,480 --> 00:23:40,350
The province organized

541
00:23:40,350 --> 00:23:41,640
an inspection team

542
00:23:41,830 --> 00:23:43,030
to come to Shenzhen.

543
00:23:43,030 --> 00:23:43,680
As the one

544
00:23:43,680 --> 00:23:44,510
in charge of

545
00:23:44,510 --> 00:23:45,590
the Jing River Bridge project,

546
00:23:46,160 --> 00:23:47,240
I didn't have to join.

547
00:23:48,480 --> 00:23:49,920
But since you're here,

548
00:23:50,270 --> 00:23:51,550
I wanted to check on you.

549
00:23:52,310 --> 00:23:53,480
I do have selfish motives.

550
00:23:54,590 --> 00:23:56,110
But it's not an abuse of power.

551
00:23:59,270 --> 00:24:00,240
Before I came,

552
00:24:00,270 --> 00:24:01,750
I went to the university

553
00:24:02,400 --> 00:24:03,200
and requested

554
00:24:04,200 --> 00:24:05,750
a certificate of enrollment.

555
00:24:06,240 --> 00:24:07,830
Though it's not an academic certificate,

556
00:24:08,790 --> 00:24:10,440
it clearly states

557
00:24:11,550 --> 00:24:13,310
you were admitted through

558
00:24:13,880 --> 00:24:15,240
the entrance examination.

559
00:24:16,000 --> 00:24:16,680
Three years of study.

560
00:24:17,110 --> 00:24:18,400
Excellent grades in the first two.

561
00:24:19,070 --> 00:24:20,400
Currently on leave of absence.

562
00:24:21,270 --> 00:24:23,110
You're making your way in Shenzhen alone.

563
00:24:24,240 --> 00:24:25,590
I think this document

564
00:24:26,070 --> 00:24:27,270
might help you.

565
00:24:33,960 --> 00:24:35,200
That's very considerate.

566
00:24:36,720 --> 00:24:37,440
Thanks.

567
00:24:41,000 --> 00:24:42,440
You're my only child.

568
00:24:44,000 --> 00:24:45,110
I really don't know

569
00:24:45,110 --> 00:24:46,640
how else I can help you.

570
00:24:47,240 --> 00:24:49,200
You've already done enough.

571
00:24:50,590 --> 00:24:51,070
By the way,

572
00:24:52,640 --> 00:24:53,720
Grandma Yu heard

573
00:24:54,960 --> 00:24:55,920
you rented a place

574
00:24:55,920 --> 00:24:57,110
in Shenzhen alone and wanted

575
00:24:57,830 --> 00:24:59,070
to come take care of you.

576
00:24:59,590 --> 00:25:00,920
I thought about it

577
00:25:01,640 --> 00:25:02,720
and refused.

578
00:25:04,720 --> 00:25:05,960
Coming to Shenzhen

579
00:25:05,960 --> 00:25:07,270
was your own decision.

580
00:25:08,880 --> 00:25:10,640
So you must prove it was

581
00:25:11,640 --> 00:25:13,240
the right decision with your own

582
00:25:13,240 --> 00:25:13,960
capability.

583
00:25:16,720 --> 00:25:18,440
Please tell Grandma Yu

584
00:25:19,000 --> 00:25:20,110
I'm doing fine here.

585
00:25:20,160 --> 00:25:21,200
Tell her to take care.

586
00:25:21,880 --> 00:25:22,550
When I move

587
00:25:22,680 --> 00:25:24,070
into a bigger house,

588
00:25:24,480 --> 00:25:25,680
I'll bring her over.

589
00:25:29,920 --> 00:25:31,000
You haven't had dinner.

590
00:25:31,240 --> 00:25:32,030
Aren't you hungry?

591
00:25:33,510 --> 00:25:34,590
If you have

592
00:25:34,750 --> 00:25:36,000
something simple,

593
00:25:36,000 --> 00:25:37,310
I'll have some.

594
00:25:38,880 --> 00:25:40,070
Only instant noodles.

595
00:25:40,510 --> 00:25:41,240
That's okay.

596
00:25:42,310 --> 00:25:43,240
I'll make some.

597
00:25:58,640 --> 00:25:59,200
See?

598
00:25:59,310 --> 00:26:01,110
Shenzhen's traffic is so convenient.

599
00:26:04,030 --> 00:26:05,480
See you, then.

600
00:26:09,790 --> 00:26:10,480
Li,

601
00:26:11,680 --> 00:26:12,550
if you have time,

602
00:26:12,550 --> 00:26:14,110
come to Yu County with Wanzhi.

603
00:26:14,640 --> 00:26:15,400
We'll definitely

604
00:26:15,400 --> 00:26:16,480
show our hospitality

605
00:26:16,790 --> 00:26:17,680
and treat you well.

606
00:26:18,200 --> 00:26:19,000
Thank you, Mr. Meng.

607
00:26:19,270 --> 00:26:20,110
Have a safe trip.

608
00:26:20,310 --> 00:26:20,680
Alright.

609
00:26:20,720 --> 00:26:21,350
Goodbye, Mr. Xiao.

610
00:26:21,680 --> 00:26:22,200
Goodbye.

611
00:26:31,200 --> 00:26:31,750
Go back now.

612
00:26:32,750 --> 00:26:33,590
Don't forget to call me.

613
00:26:35,440 --> 00:26:36,440
Goodbye, Mr. Meng.

614
00:26:52,350 --> 00:26:53,070
Why didn't I hear

615
00:26:53,070 --> 00:26:54,400
you call him Dad even once?

616
00:27:11,270 --> 00:27:12,550
Stop spacing out and go to bed.

617
00:27:19,160 --> 00:27:20,030
What is this?

618
00:27:21,200 --> 00:27:21,880
Wanzhi?

619
00:27:23,830 --> 00:27:24,830
So much money here!

620
00:27:35,880 --> 00:27:36,590
He must have left it

621
00:27:36,590 --> 00:27:37,830
while I was cooking instant noodles.

622
00:27:39,270 --> 00:27:40,350
Your dad's so nice.

623
00:27:42,550 --> 00:27:43,160
But...

624
00:27:44,070 --> 00:27:45,350
I know you're self-reliant.

625
00:27:46,070 --> 00:27:47,070
Let's send the money back

626
00:27:47,790 --> 00:27:48,750
at the post office

627
00:27:48,750 --> 00:27:49,350
tomorrow.

628
00:27:50,790 --> 00:27:52,200
Then he'll really be sad.

629
00:27:59,310 --> 00:28:01,110
You're making your way in Shenzhen alone.

630
00:28:02,310 --> 00:28:03,590
I think this document

631
00:28:04,110 --> 00:28:05,240
might help you.

632
00:28:05,960 --> 00:28:07,480
Making my way...

633
00:28:08,680 --> 00:28:09,400
What did you say?

634
00:28:10,310 --> 00:28:11,480
He doesn't think

635
00:28:12,510 --> 00:28:13,240
I'm fooling around.

636
00:28:13,830 --> 00:28:15,350
He didn't ask about my job

637
00:28:15,350 --> 00:28:17,070
or my salary.

638
00:28:18,920 --> 00:28:19,480
Juan,

639
00:28:22,270 --> 00:28:23,310
have we ever really tried

640
00:28:24,310 --> 00:28:25,400
to accomplish something here?

641
00:28:26,640 --> 00:28:27,480
Accomplish something?

642
00:28:29,310 --> 00:28:30,480
What do you mean?

643
00:28:33,200 --> 00:28:33,720
We're not going

644
00:28:33,720 --> 00:28:34,680
to the job market tomorrow.

645
00:28:35,070 --> 00:28:36,000
Let's dress up

646
00:28:36,000 --> 00:28:36,830
and explore Shenzhen.

647
00:28:37,310 --> 00:28:38,110
We'll go

648
00:28:38,110 --> 00:28:39,030
wherever it's lively

649
00:28:39,030 --> 00:28:40,030
and people spend big.

650
00:28:53,110 --> 00:28:54,680
This is our store's new

651
00:28:54,750 --> 00:28:55,510
plaid coat.

652
00:28:58,880 --> 00:28:59,400
Another one.

653
00:29:00,110 --> 00:29:00,720
Oh, miss,

654
00:29:00,790 --> 00:29:02,550
you look great in this!

655
00:29:02,830 --> 00:29:05,440
This outfit looks nice.

656
00:29:05,680 --> 00:29:06,750
But on you,

657
00:29:07,550 --> 00:29:08,720
it's only average.

658
00:29:08,750 --> 00:29:10,110
I... I also think it's average.

659
00:29:11,920 --> 00:29:13,640
Pick me another elegant one.

660
00:29:13,720 --> 00:29:14,510
Give me a second.

661
00:29:16,750 --> 00:29:17,960
Three thousand!

662
00:29:25,000 --> 00:29:26,920
Our restaurant specializes in seafood.

663
00:29:27,240 --> 00:29:27,920
Look over there.

664
00:29:28,070 --> 00:29:30,310
We also have sea bass here.

665
00:29:33,240 --> 00:29:33,920
Juan,

666
00:29:34,680 --> 00:29:35,640
we've been eating seafood

667
00:29:35,640 --> 00:29:36,270
all week.

668
00:29:36,310 --> 00:29:37,550
Maybe let's try something else?

669
00:29:50,160 --> 00:29:51,160
It's more comfortable here.

670
00:29:52,030 --> 00:29:53,400
The past two days were awful.

671
00:29:53,400 --> 00:29:54,550
I can't pretend anymore.

672
00:29:55,310 --> 00:29:56,110
We aren't pretending.

673
00:29:56,240 --> 00:29:57,480
We're doing a survey.

674
00:29:57,640 --> 00:29:58,550
How else can we know

675
00:29:58,550 --> 00:29:59,400
how others do business

676
00:29:59,400 --> 00:30:00,590
and how expensive

677
00:30:00,960 --> 00:30:02,110
big stores are without seeing

678
00:30:02,110 --> 00:30:03,000
for ourselves?

679
00:30:04,310 --> 00:30:05,590
Tell me, with prices that high,

680
00:30:05,640 --> 00:30:06,510
who would buy them?

681
00:30:07,400 --> 00:30:08,350
Many people would.

682
00:30:08,790 --> 00:30:10,110
There are different consumer groups.

683
00:30:10,680 --> 00:30:11,070
Also,

684
00:30:11,310 --> 00:30:12,440
we inspected four

685
00:30:12,440 --> 00:30:13,350
restaurants today.

686
00:30:13,750 --> 00:30:15,640
The pricier, the more popular.

687
00:30:16,110 --> 00:30:16,790
So?

688
00:30:17,070 --> 00:30:18,240
Should we open a pricey one?

689
00:30:20,030 --> 00:30:20,880
That's not realistic.

690
00:30:21,110 --> 00:30:22,590
We'd need a lot of capital.

691
00:30:25,310 --> 00:30:25,830
You know what?

692
00:30:27,310 --> 00:30:28,720
This sandwich tastes really good.

693
00:30:29,720 --> 00:30:31,400
And we'd need a brand...

694
00:30:31,720 --> 00:30:32,880
Franchise fee...

695
00:30:34,200 --> 00:30:35,720
All prices we can't afford.

696
00:30:37,480 --> 00:30:38,960
You've looked into that too?

697
00:30:39,200 --> 00:30:40,680
I talked to the waitress.

698
00:30:43,110 --> 00:30:43,480
I think

699
00:30:43,480 --> 00:30:45,200
we should change direction.

700
00:30:46,960 --> 00:30:48,310
We need to be more down-to-earth.

701
00:30:51,240 --> 00:30:53,790
(Dongmen was still
a free market back then.)

702
00:30:54,440 --> 00:30:55,480
(It was a business jungle,)

703
00:30:55,480 --> 00:30:57,750
(full of raw passion,)

704
00:30:58,160 --> 00:31:00,030
(trends, and opportunities.)

705
00:31:00,590 --> 00:31:02,160
(I was instantly drawn in.)

706
00:31:02,920 --> 00:31:04,310
(But I didn't know)

707
00:31:04,880 --> 00:31:06,510
(it was a place of dreams,)

708
00:31:06,880 --> 00:31:08,200
(and of ruin.)

709
00:31:09,030 --> 00:31:10,550
(Making my way in Shenzhen...)

710
00:31:11,070 --> 00:31:12,720
(I've been too naive.)

711
00:31:13,830 --> 00:31:15,110
So many people!

712
00:31:16,110 --> 00:31:17,240
We've come to the right place.

713
00:31:18,160 --> 00:31:19,000
Five pieces will do.

714
00:31:23,400 --> 00:31:24,590
Yes, all new styles.

715
00:31:27,070 --> 00:31:28,000
Sir?

716
00:31:29,590 --> 00:31:30,680
How much is this one?

717
00:31:31,550 --> 00:31:33,310
Sorry, wholesale only.

718
00:31:33,400 --> 00:31:34,790
No orders under ten pieces.

719
00:31:34,790 --> 00:31:35,270
Sir!

720
00:31:37,110 --> 00:31:39,110
Ten pieces are too few. I'll take twenty.

721
00:31:42,960 --> 00:31:43,640
Hey, pretty.

722
00:31:44,240 --> 00:31:45,680
I haven't seen you before.

723
00:31:46,240 --> 00:31:46,880
Where do you sell?

724
00:31:47,000 --> 00:31:48,070
Wuhan or Chengdu?

725
00:31:48,960 --> 00:31:50,070
I haven't decided yet.

726
00:31:50,350 --> 00:31:51,270
Settle the price first.

727
00:31:52,830 --> 00:31:53,640
Then, you must be

728
00:31:53,640 --> 00:31:54,790
joking with me.

729
00:31:57,350 --> 00:31:59,070
However, you look very pretty.

730
00:31:59,160 --> 00:32:00,480
Maybe we can have dinner together.

731
00:32:01,270 --> 00:32:02,440
We're talking business.

732
00:32:02,440 --> 00:32:03,640
Don't change the subject.

733
00:32:04,160 --> 00:32:05,720
You don't even know where to sell.

734
00:32:05,720 --> 00:32:06,590
But making purchases?

735
00:32:07,160 --> 00:32:08,240
You think I can't tell?

736
00:32:08,680 --> 00:32:09,590
College students, right?

737
00:32:10,440 --> 00:32:11,510
Working on your survey report

738
00:32:11,510 --> 00:32:12,680
or something, aren't you?

739
00:32:13,030 --> 00:32:14,350
I don't have time for this.

740
00:32:14,400 --> 00:32:15,110
Go somewhere else.

741
00:32:17,400 --> 00:32:19,160
We've really come to the right place.

742
00:32:19,400 --> 00:32:19,960
Really?

743
00:32:27,920 --> 00:32:29,750
With the gradual relaxation

744
00:32:29,750 --> 00:32:31,000
of various policies

745
00:32:31,030 --> 00:32:32,480
and the continuous improvement

746
00:32:32,480 --> 00:32:33,440
of living standards,

747
00:32:33,830 --> 00:32:35,750
Shenzhen is making great strides

748
00:32:35,750 --> 00:32:38,200
towards becoming a world-class city.

749
00:32:40,070 --> 00:32:40,590
Li Juan!

750
00:32:40,960 --> 00:32:41,440
What is it?

751
00:32:41,640 --> 00:32:43,000
Applause is needed here.

752
00:32:43,790 --> 00:32:45,240
What applause?

753
00:32:45,750 --> 00:32:47,440
What's that got to do with us?

754
00:32:47,680 --> 00:32:48,350
Wanzhi,

755
00:32:49,070 --> 00:32:50,680
I feel quite insecure this way.

756
00:32:50,920 --> 00:32:52,400
Maybe you keep surveying,

757
00:32:52,550 --> 00:32:53,200
and I'll find

758
00:32:53,200 --> 00:32:54,480
a part-time job first, okay?

759
00:32:55,030 --> 00:32:55,830
No.

760
00:32:56,350 --> 00:32:58,240
Of course it matters to us.

761
00:32:58,510 --> 00:32:59,590
First, it proves

762
00:32:59,680 --> 00:33:00,680
it was the right decision

763
00:33:00,920 --> 00:33:01,920
to come to Shenzhen.

764
00:33:02,440 --> 00:33:04,680
If you make the right choices in life,

765
00:33:04,790 --> 00:33:06,270
you're already halfway to success,

766
00:33:06,790 --> 00:33:08,270
said the famous philosopher...

767
00:33:09,000 --> 00:33:09,720
Look at me!

768
00:33:11,030 --> 00:33:12,440
The famous philosopher Fang Wanzhi!

769
00:33:12,590 --> 00:33:13,240
Applause!

770
00:33:17,400 --> 00:33:18,960
And as for direction,

771
00:33:19,400 --> 00:33:21,200
even though we've worked
in a canteen before,

772
00:33:21,510 --> 00:33:24,000
running a restaurant is too costly

773
00:33:24,200 --> 00:33:25,240
and too complicated.

774
00:33:25,270 --> 00:33:25,920
We won't succeed.

775
00:33:26,160 --> 00:33:28,880
And big moves like starting

776
00:33:28,880 --> 00:33:30,880
a trading company or a factory

777
00:33:31,070 --> 00:33:32,350
are our future goals.

778
00:33:32,510 --> 00:33:34,160
So, what suits us now

779
00:33:34,400 --> 00:33:35,590
is street vending.

780
00:33:35,960 --> 00:33:36,720
Street vending?

781
00:33:37,680 --> 00:33:38,400
Why?

782
00:33:39,310 --> 00:33:40,110
We don't have

783
00:33:40,110 --> 00:33:41,270
business experience,

784
00:33:41,400 --> 00:33:42,960
but we did work at a clothing factory.

785
00:33:43,310 --> 00:33:45,270
Moreover, I'm confident

786
00:33:45,270 --> 00:33:46,640
in my eye for style.

787
00:33:46,830 --> 00:33:48,310
I'll do well choosing products.

788
00:33:48,880 --> 00:33:49,640
Agree!

789
00:33:50,240 --> 00:33:50,720
Come over.

790
00:33:52,350 --> 00:33:54,270
Dongmen Street in Luohu District,

791
00:33:54,270 --> 00:33:55,000
a hot shopping spot.

792
00:33:55,200 --> 00:33:56,720
Customer traffic there consistently

793
00:33:56,720 --> 00:33:58,030
ranks first in Shenzhen.

794
00:33:58,440 --> 00:34:00,000
We can rent a good store

795
00:34:00,000 --> 00:34:00,830
in Dongmen,

796
00:34:00,960 --> 00:34:01,920
sell clothes,

797
00:34:02,070 --> 00:34:03,310
and start our own business!

798
00:34:03,550 --> 00:34:04,400
Start our business?

799
00:34:05,110 --> 00:34:06,400
Is it really that easy?

800
00:34:07,350 --> 00:34:08,150
Are you confident?

801
00:34:08,400 --> 00:34:09,230
Following you,

802
00:34:09,230 --> 00:34:10,480
I'm definitely confident.

803
00:34:10,480 --> 00:34:11,630
I'll work for you, boss.

804
00:34:12,030 --> 00:34:13,440
We're doing this together.

805
00:34:13,630 --> 00:34:15,110
You'll be a shareholder.

806
00:34:15,400 --> 00:34:16,960
I can't be a shareholder.

807
00:34:16,960 --> 00:34:18,230
I don't have money.

808
00:34:18,230 --> 00:34:19,280
And I know nothing.

809
00:34:20,360 --> 00:34:21,320
But you give me

810
00:34:21,320 --> 00:34:22,320
the greatest support.

811
00:34:22,670 --> 00:34:23,760
You're my drive.

812
00:34:24,960 --> 00:34:25,590
Wait!

813
00:34:29,960 --> 00:34:30,590
Wanzhi,

814
00:34:32,880 --> 00:34:33,670
I just sent money

815
00:34:33,800 --> 00:34:35,190
back to my home last month.

816
00:34:35,360 --> 00:34:36,360
I only have 1,000 left.

817
00:34:36,840 --> 00:34:38,320
I know how much capital you have.

818
00:34:39,550 --> 00:34:40,710
Just give me two percent.

819
00:34:41,840 --> 00:34:42,920
Absolutely not!

820
00:34:44,320 --> 00:34:45,840
I'll take the 1,000

821
00:34:46,000 --> 00:34:47,280
and give you 20% shares.

822
00:34:47,400 --> 00:34:48,110
No.

823
00:34:48,590 --> 00:34:49,510
That doesn't make sense.

824
00:34:50,590 --> 00:34:51,150
Fine, then.

825
00:34:51,510 --> 00:34:52,070
I'll give you

826
00:34:52,070 --> 00:34:53,110
a fixed salary every month,

827
00:34:53,190 --> 00:34:54,230
plus 10% shares.

828
00:34:54,510 --> 00:34:55,840
That's too much!

829
00:34:55,920 --> 00:34:57,000
It's not.

830
00:34:57,550 --> 00:34:58,480
Even a helper

831
00:34:58,480 --> 00:34:59,070
at the stall

832
00:34:59,070 --> 00:35:00,230
gets 10% commission.

833
00:35:00,480 --> 00:35:01,550
We're not like that.

834
00:35:01,550 --> 00:35:02,670
You're paying me a salary.

835
00:35:02,840 --> 00:35:03,280
Listen,

836
00:35:03,550 --> 00:35:04,440
I'll take five percent.

837
00:35:04,800 --> 00:35:06,150
Seven point five.

838
00:35:06,280 --> 00:35:06,760
It's settled.

839
00:35:06,920 --> 00:35:07,670
Dividends will be

840
00:35:07,710 --> 00:35:08,960
distributed every three months.

841
00:35:15,440 --> 00:35:16,510
What's so funny?

842
00:35:19,550 --> 00:35:21,030
Li Juan, why are you laughing?

843
00:35:21,030 --> 00:35:21,880
What do you think?

844
00:35:22,230 --> 00:35:23,400
Oh my! Fang Wanzhi!

845
00:35:23,630 --> 00:35:24,150
Come on!

846
00:35:24,400 --> 00:35:25,150
We haven't even

847
00:35:25,150 --> 00:35:26,190
started doing anything yet,

848
00:35:26,190 --> 00:35:28,000
and we're already talking about dividends?

849
00:35:48,480 --> 00:35:49,320
Sir?

850
00:35:49,480 --> 00:35:50,150
Sir!

851
00:35:50,800 --> 00:35:51,360
Sir!

852
00:35:51,920 --> 00:35:52,710
I'm here.

853
00:35:58,880 --> 00:35:59,320
You...

854
00:36:00,070 --> 00:36:01,480
I saw you yesterday, right?

855
00:36:02,320 --> 00:36:02,840
Yeah.

856
00:36:03,630 --> 00:36:04,480
What's your name?

857
00:36:05,400 --> 00:36:06,880
Just call him Mr. Gold Tooth.

858
00:36:07,360 --> 00:36:07,880
Right.

859
00:36:08,280 --> 00:36:08,960
Mr. Gold Tooth,

860
00:36:10,070 --> 00:36:11,630
do you own this stall?

861
00:36:12,000 --> 00:36:12,440
Yes.

862
00:36:13,000 --> 00:36:14,440
These stalls around here belong to me.

863
00:36:15,760 --> 00:36:16,440
Wanna rent one?

864
00:36:17,670 --> 00:36:18,280
What's the rent?

865
00:36:19,800 --> 00:36:20,710
One-year lease,

866
00:36:20,800 --> 00:36:21,960
half paid upfront.

867
00:36:22,030 --> 00:36:23,110
Fifty thousand yuan a year?

868
00:36:23,110 --> 00:36:24,590
That's too expensive!

869
00:36:24,760 --> 00:36:26,630
Are you kidding me, lady?

870
00:36:27,150 --> 00:36:28,440
It's 500,000 yuan!

871
00:36:28,800 --> 00:36:30,880
If you want to rent here,

872
00:36:31,000 --> 00:36:32,280
you should have asked

873
00:36:32,280 --> 00:36:33,400
about the market price first.

874
00:36:33,630 --> 00:36:34,840
I have.

875
00:36:35,230 --> 00:36:36,440
But 500,000 a year

876
00:36:36,440 --> 00:36:37,360
is too much!

877
00:36:37,510 --> 00:36:38,320
Is your stall made

878
00:36:38,320 --> 00:36:39,360
of gold or something?

879
00:36:39,630 --> 00:36:41,230
My friend didn't mean anything.

880
00:36:41,230 --> 00:36:42,360
Why are you so harsh?

881
00:36:42,510 --> 00:36:43,630
With money, I can always

882
00:36:43,630 --> 00:36:44,710
find a good store to rent.

883
00:36:45,000 --> 00:36:45,400
Let's go!

884
00:36:51,480 --> 00:36:52,280
Dongmen is big.

885
00:36:52,280 --> 00:36:53,590
There isn't just one market.

886
00:36:54,630 --> 00:36:56,030
Let's check other corners.

887
00:36:56,760 --> 00:36:57,280
Okay.

888
00:36:58,670 --> 00:36:59,280
Wanzhi,

889
00:37:00,030 --> 00:37:00,880
I think that

890
00:37:01,550 --> 00:37:02,590
to rent a store here,

891
00:37:02,590 --> 00:37:03,280
the rent

892
00:37:03,280 --> 00:37:04,510
must be under 10,000 a year.

893
00:37:04,670 --> 00:37:05,840
Or it'd be too expensive.

894
00:37:06,150 --> 00:37:07,630
If business doesn't go well,

895
00:37:07,840 --> 00:37:09,280
you won't lose too much this way.

896
00:37:15,840 --> 00:37:16,510
Fang?

897
00:37:16,960 --> 00:37:17,670
Any buyers yet?

898
00:37:18,840 --> 00:37:19,800
Not yet.

899
00:37:21,000 --> 00:37:21,360
Ma'am,

900
00:37:21,360 --> 00:37:22,510
your store is doing well.

901
00:37:22,840 --> 00:37:23,630
You've sold several

902
00:37:23,630 --> 00:37:24,760
pairs of socks this morning.

903
00:37:25,230 --> 00:37:26,480
One yuan for a pair.

904
00:37:26,550 --> 00:37:27,510
The profit is only 30%.

905
00:37:27,670 --> 00:37:28,760
How much can I make?

906
00:37:29,440 --> 00:37:31,150
Your store isn't making money?

907
00:37:32,030 --> 00:37:33,510
I'm just helping at the stall.

908
00:37:33,670 --> 00:37:35,280
If the boss isn't anxious,
why should I be?

909
00:37:35,920 --> 00:37:36,670
Besides,

910
00:37:37,000 --> 00:37:37,480
this street

911
00:37:37,480 --> 00:37:38,760
isn't as popular.

912
00:37:39,670 --> 00:37:41,030
Not many stores here make money.

913
00:37:48,000 --> 00:37:48,550
Sir,

914
00:37:48,880 --> 00:37:50,440
newly launched clothes!

915
00:37:50,440 --> 00:37:51,150
On a discount!

916
00:37:51,190 --> 00:37:51,670
Come on!

917
00:37:51,800 --> 00:37:52,280
Try them...

918
00:37:52,440 --> 00:37:53,070
What are you doing?

919
00:37:54,070 --> 00:37:55,320
Are you trying to rob me?

920
00:37:59,480 --> 00:38:00,880
That's not how you do business.

921
00:38:03,760 --> 00:38:04,360
Lady,

922
00:38:04,510 --> 00:38:06,030
can you maybe tell us

923
00:38:06,030 --> 00:38:07,320
what we should do?

924
00:38:07,840 --> 00:38:09,280
You need to read your customers.

925
00:38:09,880 --> 00:38:10,920
Only approach customers

926
00:38:10,960 --> 00:38:12,280
when they are interested

927
00:38:12,320 --> 00:38:13,550
in your items.

928
00:38:14,920 --> 00:38:17,110
There aren't many people on this street.

929
00:38:17,550 --> 00:38:18,630
I see you haven't made

930
00:38:18,630 --> 00:38:19,510
a single sale.

931
00:38:20,920 --> 00:38:21,510
Miss?

932
00:38:22,440 --> 00:38:23,440
Sir, you came!

933
00:38:23,710 --> 00:38:24,280
Yes.

934
00:38:24,400 --> 00:38:25,630
Here, it's all prepared.

935
00:38:26,510 --> 00:38:26,880
Here.

936
00:38:27,510 --> 00:38:28,400
Oh, let me handle it.

937
00:38:31,070 --> 00:38:31,480
Sir,

938
00:38:32,960 --> 00:38:33,440
this one.

939
00:38:33,630 --> 00:38:34,510
This is newly arrived.

940
00:38:34,760 --> 00:38:36,000
Very tender tea leaves.

941
00:38:36,030 --> 00:38:36,960
Rich fragrance.

942
00:38:36,960 --> 00:38:37,840
Excellent quality.

943
00:38:37,920 --> 00:38:38,670
I'll have some.

944
00:38:38,760 --> 00:38:39,190
Alright!

945
00:38:40,360 --> 00:38:41,000
It's fine.

946
00:38:41,000 --> 00:38:41,550
Here, let me.

947
00:38:42,880 --> 00:38:43,550
How much?

948
00:38:44,480 --> 00:38:44,960
Sir,

949
00:38:46,880 --> 00:38:48,320
these two are new as well.

950
00:38:48,440 --> 00:38:49,590
Here, try some for free.

951
00:38:50,320 --> 00:38:51,960
And this one, your boss' favorite.

952
00:38:52,030 --> 00:38:52,920
I've packed 250 grams.

953
00:38:53,360 --> 00:38:53,840
Thanks.

954
00:39:00,320 --> 00:39:00,760
Here.

955
00:39:01,360 --> 00:39:01,800
Thank you.

956
00:39:02,150 --> 00:39:03,150
Invoice at month's end,

957
00:39:03,150 --> 00:39:03,590
right?

958
00:39:03,630 --> 00:39:04,070
Right.

959
00:39:04,760 --> 00:39:05,320
Safe trip!

960
00:39:05,400 --> 00:39:06,230
Alright. Leaving.

961
00:39:06,280 --> 00:39:06,710
Take care.

962
00:39:12,480 --> 00:39:14,630
You need regular customers.

963
00:39:15,280 --> 00:39:16,230
He's my big customer.

964
00:39:16,880 --> 00:39:17,960
Who is he?

965
00:39:17,960 --> 00:39:19,670
Buying so much tea at once?

966
00:39:19,840 --> 00:39:21,320
Their factory has thousands of workers.

967
00:39:21,480 --> 00:39:22,400
And the boss

968
00:39:22,590 --> 00:39:23,800
treats them to tea every day.

969
00:39:24,440 --> 00:39:25,710
He's in charge of procurement.

970
00:39:26,110 --> 00:39:27,670
He comes to restock every three days.

971
00:39:31,510 --> 00:39:32,800
Don't listen to that sock seller.

972
00:39:33,190 --> 00:39:34,440
It's not her own business,

973
00:39:34,510 --> 00:39:35,550
so she doesn't care.

974
00:39:37,030 --> 00:39:38,710
Even with fewer crowds here,

975
00:39:38,960 --> 00:39:39,920
if you put in effort,

976
00:39:40,190 --> 00:39:41,400
you'll still make money.

977
00:39:42,000 --> 00:39:43,230
It's just a matter of how much.

978
00:39:44,760 --> 00:39:46,030
Thank you for teaching us.

979
00:39:47,110 --> 00:39:48,480
I'm not teaching you anything.

980
00:39:48,510 --> 00:39:49,510
I've just been

981
00:39:50,030 --> 00:39:51,280
in business a few years longer.

982
00:39:52,280 --> 00:39:52,920
Thanks.

983
00:40:03,400 --> 00:40:04,840
Watch out! Be careful! Taking a turn.

984
00:40:05,360 --> 00:40:06,070
Be careful.

985
00:40:07,030 --> 00:40:07,550
Push!

986
00:40:07,960 --> 00:40:09,150
Push! I'm out of strength!

987
00:40:09,150 --> 00:40:11,030
-Here we go!
-Come on!

988
00:40:11,960 --> 00:40:13,110
Come on, Wanzhi!

989
00:40:15,960 --> 00:40:17,510
Hey, everyone, check it out!

990
00:40:17,590 --> 00:40:18,280
Here, lady.

991
00:40:18,480 --> 00:40:20,110
Newly launched jeans!

992
00:40:20,150 --> 00:40:21,030
Look at the style!

993
00:40:21,110 --> 00:40:22,590
Our store just opened.

994
00:40:22,710 --> 00:40:23,440
We're on promotion.

995
00:40:24,000 --> 00:40:25,280
It makes you look especially...

996
00:40:25,320 --> 00:40:25,880
Fair-skinned!

997
00:40:25,880 --> 00:40:26,800
Yes, fair-skinned!

998
00:40:26,800 --> 00:40:27,590
This is very popular.

999
00:40:27,590 --> 00:40:28,030
Yes.

1000
00:40:28,150 --> 00:40:28,920
Check out the others!

1001
00:40:28,920 --> 00:40:29,710
Many other styles...

1002
00:40:29,710 --> 00:40:30,550
We have other styles!

1003
00:40:30,550 --> 00:40:31,110
Lady?

1004
00:40:34,920 --> 00:40:36,440
These denim jackets and jeans

1005
00:40:36,480 --> 00:40:37,920
are of very good quality.

1006
00:40:38,400 --> 00:40:39,670
Especially the jeans.

1007
00:40:39,670 --> 00:40:41,480
They look very good on you!

1008
00:40:41,480 --> 00:40:41,960
See?

1009
00:40:42,000 --> 00:40:43,000
Check the quality.

1010
00:40:43,000 --> 00:40:43,510
Here.

1011
00:40:43,760 --> 00:40:44,480
Let me through.

1012
00:40:44,480 --> 00:40:45,030
Nothing pricey.

1013
00:40:45,030 --> 00:40:45,960
If you like them,

1014
00:40:45,960 --> 00:40:46,840
I'll take you over.

1015
00:40:46,840 --> 00:40:48,280
Move on! Stop crowding here!

1016
00:40:48,320 --> 00:40:49,630
Scatter!

1017
00:40:49,960 --> 00:40:51,030
Scatter now!

1018
00:40:53,800 --> 00:40:54,440
Hey, girls,

1019
00:40:55,480 --> 00:40:57,480
this is against the rules.

1020
00:40:57,760 --> 00:40:59,360
The administrator will fine you.

1021
00:40:59,710 --> 00:41:01,440
We aren't in front of your store.

1022
00:41:01,670 --> 00:41:03,710
But this is also the market.

1023
00:41:04,000 --> 00:41:05,230
There are rules

1024
00:41:05,230 --> 00:41:06,880
in the market, you know.

1025
00:41:06,880 --> 00:41:08,960
It's not my decision.

1026
00:41:12,960 --> 00:41:14,630
Not the first time doing this, huh?

1027
00:41:15,510 --> 00:41:16,670
This is against

1028
00:41:16,670 --> 00:41:17,400
the regulations here.

1029
00:41:17,670 --> 00:41:18,280
The fine is 50.

1030
00:41:18,760 --> 00:41:19,320
Fifty?

1031
00:41:19,590 --> 00:41:21,510
Why fine her less? Because she's pretty?

1032
00:41:22,150 --> 00:41:22,960
Didn't the last one

1033
00:41:22,960 --> 00:41:24,550
get fined 100 yuan?

1034
00:41:27,360 --> 00:41:28,480
Just pay up.

1035
00:41:31,110 --> 00:41:31,630
Lady!

1036
00:41:32,230 --> 00:41:32,710
Lady!

1037
00:41:33,070 --> 00:41:33,960
Wait up!

1038
00:41:35,800 --> 00:41:36,630
Why don't you

1039
00:41:36,630 --> 00:41:37,590
just rent my store?

1040
00:41:37,800 --> 00:41:39,000
I'll give you an 80% discount.

1041
00:41:39,710 --> 00:41:40,440
Sir,

1042
00:41:40,920 --> 00:41:42,630
I can pay maybe 50.

1043
00:41:42,960 --> 00:41:43,710
But 500,000?

1044
00:41:44,110 --> 00:41:44,760
I can never

1045
00:41:44,760 --> 00:41:45,480
take out that much.

1046
00:41:46,230 --> 00:41:48,440
But my place has good foot traffic.

1047
00:41:48,670 --> 00:41:49,320
You can earn

1048
00:41:49,320 --> 00:41:51,230
the 500,000 yuan back in no time.

1049
00:41:51,670 --> 00:41:53,400
Your store has no crowd there.

1050
00:41:53,400 --> 00:41:55,360
Cheap, but not a good bargain.

1051
00:41:55,550 --> 00:41:56,440
I don't buy it.

1052
00:41:58,630 --> 00:41:59,710
Why don't we make a bet?

1053
00:42:00,440 --> 00:42:01,360
By the end of the year,

1054
00:42:01,510 --> 00:42:02,360
if you make money,

1055
00:42:02,440 --> 00:42:03,550
I'll respect you forever.

1056
00:42:04,550 --> 00:42:05,550
But if you lose money,

1057
00:42:07,630 --> 00:42:08,480
be my girlfriend.

1058
00:42:08,630 --> 00:42:09,800
What the hell?

1059
00:42:09,800 --> 00:42:10,800
Taking advantage of me?

1060
00:42:11,110 --> 00:42:12,550
No way, even if you swapped that

1061
00:42:12,550 --> 00:42:13,710
gold tooth for an elephant tusk!

1062
00:42:16,710 --> 00:42:17,670
I won't lose money!

1063
00:42:34,190 --> 00:42:35,190
It's been three months.

1064
00:42:36,030 --> 00:42:37,000
We're still losing money.

1065
00:42:38,440 --> 00:42:39,280
Cut my salary.

1066
00:42:40,070 --> 00:42:41,030
I can't do that!

1067
00:42:41,150 --> 00:42:42,630
I promised you a salary.

1068
00:42:42,960 --> 00:42:44,150
But we lost money, didn't we?

1069
00:42:44,230 --> 00:42:45,360
That's on me.

1070
00:42:45,710 --> 00:42:46,670
We agreed on that.
